'''Muhammad Hussein Ali Hassan''' is a citizen of [[Morocco]] who was held in [[extrajudicial detention]] in the [[United States]] [[Guantanamo Bay detention camp]]s, in [[Cuba]].<ref name=DoDList2>[http://www.dod.mil/news/May2006/d20060515%20List.pdf list of prisoners], ''[[US Department of Defense]]'', May 15, 2006</ref> His Guantanamo [[Internment Serial Number]] is 123. [[Joint Task Force Guantanamo]] [[counter-terrorism]] analysts report he was born on December 16, 1966, in [[Selwan, Morocco|Selwan]], Morocco.
Muhammad Hussein Ali Hassan was transferred to Morocco on February 7, 2006.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://projects.nytimes.com/guantanamo/detainees/123-muhammad-hussein-ali-hassan | work=The New York Times | title=Muhammad Hussein Ali Hassan - The GuantÃ¡namo Docket}}</ref>
